1
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,000
A Di

2
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,520
Bro A Di

3
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,600
Weren't you dead?

4
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:02,760
Surprised?

5
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,880
There's an even bigger surprise.

6
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:10,800
You even brought a...

7
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,000
You even brought a Savage back.

8
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,480
Even if you survived the Valley of Death,

9
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,160
there's no way you could be this fast.

10
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,120
Smear blood on the center of my brow.

11
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,200
From now on,

12
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,840
you're my Master.

13
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,160
You're pledging fealty to me?

14
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:30,240
Slay the Yanwangchou warrior...

15
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,080
the sage who can cure numbing poison...

16
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:32,840
Remove...

17
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,200
All right, all right.

18
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:34,520
I agree.

19
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,400
Hong Ye wants to work with us.

20
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,800
Doing this...

21
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,960
you didn't get Hong Ye's approval, right?

22
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,880
You're just business partners.

23
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,480
If it fails, we'll just find someone else.

24
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,720
But you dared to kidnap Dawa in Dongba.

25
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,040
You won't be alive much longer.

26
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,000
Oops.

27
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,680
Sorry about that.

28
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,000
My hand slipped.

29
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,160
Dawa.

30
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,720
You're in our hands now.

31
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,160
Tell me,

32
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,400
if we kill you right here, right now,

33
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,280
do you think Hong Ye would care?

34
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,120
You're just his nephew,

35
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,680
not his son.

36
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:28,960
Listen up.

37
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,160
We

38
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,360
don't want to start trouble.

39
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,160
After all, in Dongba right now,

40
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,000
it's not just two sides anymore.

41
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,320
It's a three-way standoff.

42
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,000
That third side you mentioned...

43
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,600
it's not you, is it?

44
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,280
You, all by yourself?

45
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,640
You think you're worthy?

46
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,560
I'm not.

47
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,840
But my wife is.

48
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:51,840
Looks like

49
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,600
you really don't know how

50
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,880
formidable my wife is.

51
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,760
Then today I've gotta give you

52
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,720
a proper introduction.

53
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,440
Shen Xingyu.

54
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,960
Founder of Xingyu Optoelectronics.

55
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,800
Worth hundreds of millions.

56
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,520
A business heavyweight.

57
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,560
A top-tier tech genius.

58
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,440
Dawa, what's with that face?

59
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,160
Man, you really live under a rock.

60
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,480
I'm warning you.

61
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,200
If you ever target my wife again,

62
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,680
I'll send you to the Death Jungle,

63
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,560
and we'll see if you make it out alive.

64
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,680
This is my final warning.

65
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:31,720
Fine.

66
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,520
You got it.

67
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,320
I'll remember.

68
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,040
Master.

69
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,120
Those guys outside

70
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,600
I knocked them all out.

71
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,040
Nice work.

72
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,160
So,

73
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,160
if we just let Dawa go like this,

74
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,040
will Hong Ye forgive us?

75
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,240
Bro A Di.

76
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,320
Who is she?

77
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:01,160
I forgot to introduce her earlier.

78
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,680
This is Nida.

79
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,720
A new friend I just met.

80
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,520
I'm Master's woman.

81
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,480
Wherever Master goes, I go.

82
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,720
Hold on.

83
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:11,880
You're saying

84
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,760
Bro Wu Di is your Master?

85
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,400
Then I'm Bro Wu Di's good brother.

86
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,720
Does that make me your Master too?

87
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,400
You've got another woman out there now?

88
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,600
How can you face my sister?

89
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,960
Don't talk nonsense.

90
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:24,840
Nida.

91
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,560
What you said just now, out here,

92
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,120
means "wife."

93
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,880
So what?

94
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,800
In our tribe,

95
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,800
man or woman,

96
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,800
once you pledge fealty,

97
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,120
you serve your Master.

98
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,160
So,

99
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,720
I'm your woman.

100
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,640
No, no, no. When in Rome,

101
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,360
you've gotta follow the rules out here.

102
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:41,800
Darling.

103
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,360
She's the one you spoke to in the jungle,

104
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,320
the Savage woman who wanted to kill you, right?

105
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,200
What are you gonna do with her?

106
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,280
Don't go near my Master!

107
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,520
Nida.

108
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,080
Nida!

109
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:55,800
Calm down.

110
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,880
This is my wife.

111
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:57,960
She's one of us.

112
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,880
Wife, let me explain.

113
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,800
I made a deal with her.

114
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,840
I helped her detox,

115
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,080
and she led me out of the jungle.

116
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,400
But after we got out,

117
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,160
she insisted on taking me as her Master.

118
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,800
I didn't have much choice.

119
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,800
What "Master"? What...

120
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,200
What "one of us"?

121
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,480
I wanna play too!

122
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,640
Hey, Bro Wu Di,

123
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,040
don't we have a meeting this afternoon?

124
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,560
Aren't we gonna be late?

125
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,560
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

126
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,440
I've got an important meeting too.

127
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,440
I'll head over first.

128
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:23,880
Master.

129
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,200
Since you helped Wu Di,

130
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,920
if you don't have anywhere to go,

131
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,240
then stay here.

132
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,160
No.

133
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,280
I'm following Master.

134
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,600
Xingyu.

135
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,560
Have some soup.

136
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,440
The braised pork is ready.

137
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,240
I'll dish it up.

138
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,040
I'm telling you,

139
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,680
I spent ages on this braised pork.

140
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,160
It's my family's secret recipe.

141
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,200
Smells amazing.

142
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,400
I really put my heart into it.

143
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,840
Xingyu.

144
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:18,520
Your favorite braised pork.

145
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,480
Come on, try it.

146
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:20,680
Your favorite.

147
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,720
Go on, eat.

148
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,120
Nida.

149
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,080
Next time you eat, use chopsticks.

150
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,560
Don't grab it with your hands.

151
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,360
(Tomorrow Hong Ye wants to use
truth serum on Dr. Zhang)

152
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,160
(Hurry and rescue him)

153
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,440
Is this intel reliable?

154
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,480
Even though sometimes

155
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,480
the job's kinda sketchy

156
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,760
the messages he sends

157
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,760
have always been pretty solid

158
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,280
But unfortunately,

159
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,120
I just don't know who the person

160
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,000
behind all this is.

161
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,840
If that's really the case,

162
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,000
we've gotta rescue Dr. Zhang fast

163
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,320
Then here's the plan.

164
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,200
Tonight,

165
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,240
I'll go to Hong Ye's villa

166
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,840
and take a look around

167
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,120
see if there's any sign of the doctor

168
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,600
I'm going too.

169
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,680
You're not going.

170
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,040
I'm going anyway.

171
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:43,520
Why are you here?

172
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,840
Master, I told you

173
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,280
wherever you go, I go

174
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,160
Don't be ridiculous.

175
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,600
It's dangerous here.

176
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,080
It's because I know it's dangerous

177
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,080
that I had to come with you

178
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:52,960
so I can help you.

179
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,920
You really want to help me?

180
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:58,720
Then...

181
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,200
put this on.

182
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,360
With this,

183
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,920
we can stay linked from a distance

184
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,880
I can hear Master's voice in my head now

185
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:07,960
Yeah.

186
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,080
Now listen carefully.

187
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,760
Find higher ground.

188
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,760
Watch everything here.

189
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,000
We'll meet up later.

190
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:14,680
Okay.

191
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,880
Stay safe.

192
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,760
How many times have I told you?

193
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,600
This big deal with Shen Xingyu

194
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,600
don't you mess it up for me

195
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,200
They're not sincerely working with you

196
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,920
I don't want you getting played

197
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,120
Don't make me pick a new successor

198
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,280
Useless trash.

199
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,320
Who told you to get up?

200
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,520
Boss Shen.

201
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,000
I heard

202
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,400
Dawa went to see you.

203
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,280
Looks like nothing gets past Hong Ye.

204
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:05,680
Hong Ye.

205
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,280
What's wrong, Boss Shen?

206
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,320
General Dawa hit too hard

207
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,320
he dislocated my hand.

208
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,360
Bullshit!

209
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,640
I didn't even touch you.

210
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,240
General Dawa's here too.

211
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,720
Boss Shen,

212
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,960
it's just a misunderstanding.

213
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,840
This kid stepped out just now.

214
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,200
I truly didn't know.

215
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:24,600
If he upset you, Boss Shen,

216
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,400
just tell me.

217
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,320
I'll teach him a lesson.

218
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,120
Fine.

219
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,360
Next time,

220
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,120
I'll definitely exaggerate it

221
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,080
and tell Hong Ye.

222
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,800
All right, all right.

223
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,200
Since it's cleared up,

224
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,120
let's keep going.

225
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,240
Pleasure working with you.

226
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,480
Pleasure working with you, Hong Ye.

227
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,320
Sure, sure.

228
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,600
Goodbye.

229
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:46,400
Uncle, not a word of it was sincere.

230
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:51,040
You know why she said that?

231
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,640
Because Dr. Zhang is in our hands.

232
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,440
She doesn't want to offend us.

233
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,720
Got it?

234
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:03,280
She'll send someone to rescue Dr. Zhang.

235
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,680
Tighten security.

236
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,080
Why isn't Master out yet?

237
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,440
I've gotta go check.

238
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,640
We caught a Savage

239
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,920
She injured over ten of our guys.

240
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:30,720
([Speaking tribal language]
Bastards! Death Jungle curse you!)

241
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,680
What'd she say?

242
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,080
A Savage.

243
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,760
Came out of Death Jungle.

244
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,680
Zhao Wudi brought you out?

245
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,360
([Speaking tribal language]
You're not worthy to speak to me!)

246
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,200
She's pledged fealty.

247
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,200
Once she pledges fealty,

248
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,720
it's for life.

249
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,600
She's here.

250
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,720
Then Zhao Wudi

251
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,880
should be nearby, right?

252
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,760
Hold on to her tight.

253
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,600
This headset's range

254
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,520
is only 100 meters.

255
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,440
Assemble everyone, maximum alert!

256
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,080
Rats in a trap.

257
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,160
Everyone, everyone!

258
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,200
Maximum alert!

259
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,000
Zhao Wudi is in our villa!

260
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,000
Master, I played along pretty well, right?

261
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,080
I'll untie you first.

262
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:52,400
As long as you're within 3 meters of me,

263
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,160
I can smell your scent.

264
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,200
It's too dangerous here.

265
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,280
You go back first.

266
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,280
I'm going to rescue Dr. Zhang.

267
00:11:58,680 --> 00:11:59,360
Okay.

268
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,600
A Di.

269
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:06,880
Why are you here?

270
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,680
There's no time.

271
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,520
Come with me.

272
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,480
No.

273
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,680
I can't leave.
